  <summary date="2022-05-05T15:14:34Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Immigrant Investor Program Reform Act

This bill reauthorizes the EB-5 investor program through September 2025 and makes various changes to the program, such as imposing various oversight mechanisms. (EB-5 visas provide permanent resident status to qualified investors whose investments create a certain number of jobs.)</summary>
